{"title":"2025 Focus Thron² eMTB Doubles Down on Trail Riding OR Loaded Touring & Commuting","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2025-focus-thron%c2%b2-emtb-doubles-down-on-trail-riding-or-loaded-touring-commuting/","date":1741629722000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_tossed-in-the-air-1536x1024.webp\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1024\" alt=\"2025 Focus Thron² versatile alloy all-rounder ebike all-mountain trail eMTB\" /></p>\n<p>The all-new alloy Focus Thron² ebike features longer travel, trail-ready ABS, lower pricing, and a more comfortable, more versatile ride. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>It gets most of the same updates as its all-mountain Jam² <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/new-alloy-focus-jam%c2%b2-emtb-updates-all-rounder-all-mountain-ebike/\" target=\"_blank\">eMTB big brother</a>, just with slightly less travel and a heavy dose of extra versatility. This full-power all-rounder eMTB features more travel than ever before, plus a newly refined aluminum frame, the latest &amp; greatest Bosch Performance CX powertrain, several new battery options from 600Wh to 1050Wh to power any adventure, and even modern trail-capable anti-lock brakes.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_group-trail-riding.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_group-trail-riding.webp\" alt=\"2025 Focus Thron² versatile alloy all-rounder ebike all-mountain trail eMTB, trail riding\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_group-trail-riding.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_group-trail-riding-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_group-trail-riding-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_group-trail-riding-120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_group-trail-riding-768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_group-trail-riding-1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a><figcaption><em>(Photos/Focus)</em></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Whether you are looking for all-day mountain rides, everyday trips around town with the possibility to head out on tour off-the-beaten track, the new Thron² &amp; Thron² Eqp have plenty of options. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_EQP-loaded-off-road-touring.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_EQP-loaded-off-road-touring.webp\" alt=\"2025 Focus Thron² versatile alloy all-rounder ebike all-mountain trail eMTB, off-road touring\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_EQP-loaded-off-road-touring.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_EQP-loaded-off-road-touring-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_EQP-loaded-off-road-touring-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_EQP-loaded-off-road-touring-120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_EQP-loaded-off-road-touring-768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_EQP-loaded-off-road-touring-1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And you can even mix-and-match accessories to tailor your setup to how you plan to ride.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>2025 Focus Thron² versatile alloy all-mountain trail eMTB</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_wet-trail-riding.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1125\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_wet-trail-riding.webp\" alt=\"2025 Focus Thron² versatile alloy all-rounder ebike all-mountain trail eMTB, wet riding\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_wet-trail-riding.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_wet-trail-riding-297x167.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_wet-trail-riding-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_wet-trail-riding-120x68.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_wet-trail-riding-768x432.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_wet-trail-riding-1200x675.webp 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Thron² has been around for several years as the German bike brand’s do-it-all mid-travel eMTB. Focus describes the basic idea of the Thron² platform as “two [e]bikes for two different purposes”. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_entry-level.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_entry-level.webp\" alt=\"2025 Focus Thron² versatile alloy all-rounder ebike all-mountain trail eMTB, standard\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_entry-level.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_entry-level-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_entry-level-1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_entry-level-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_entry-level-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>You either get the standard Focus THRON² – a versatile full-power, plenty-of-travel all-mountain eMTB that can tackle pretty much any type of mountain biking you can throw at it. Or, you pick the fully-equipped THRON² EQP, with the exact same geo, travel &amp; trail capabilities, but with the added everyday and touring versatility provided by a solid pannier-ready rear rack, full-coverage fenders, integrated lighting, and even a kickstand. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_EQP-equipped-and-fully-loaded.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_EQP-equipped-and-fully-loaded.webp\" alt=\"2025 Focus Thron² versatile alloy all-rounder ebike all-mountain trail eMTB, EQP Equipped\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_EQP-equipped-and-fully-loaded.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_EQP-equipped-and-fully-loaded-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_EQP-equipped-and-fully-loaded-1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_EQP-equipped-and-fully-loaded-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_EQP-equipped-and-fully-loaded-768x576.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Or, the beauty of it all, the standard models can be added onto down the trail if you want any or all of that extra accessory versatility.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>All that great versatility is unchanged. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, it just gets a big functional update and lower price points.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>What’s new?</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><div>\n\n</div></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, with 140mm of four-bar F.O.L.D. rear wheel travel matched to 150mm forks, this more burly updated 2025 Focus Thron² ebike has 10-20mm more travel than the previous version. Combine that with a slack 66° headtube, middle-of-the-road 75.5° seat angle, long-ish Reach figures, taller Stack than before, and relatively long 455mm rear end… and this is going to be a properly trail-capable eMTB no matter what type of build you end up with.  </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_600Wh-battery-and-250Wh-range-extender.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1152\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_600Wh-battery-and-250Wh-range-extender-1536x1152.webp\" alt=\"2025 Focus Thron² versatile alloy all-rounder ebike all-mountain trail eMTB, 600Wh battery + 250Wh range extender\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_600Wh-battery-and-250Wh-range-extender-1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_600Wh-battery-and-250Wh-range-extender-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_600Wh-battery-and-250Wh-range-extender-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_600Wh-battery-and-250Wh-range-extender-768x576.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_600Wh-battery-and-250Wh-range-extender.webp 2000w\" /></a><figcaption>600Wh internal battery + 250Wh range extender</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_800Wh-battery.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1152\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_800Wh-battery-1536x1152.webp\" alt=\"2025 Focus Thron² versatile alloy all-rounder ebike all-mountain trail eMTB, 800Wh battery\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_800Wh-battery-1536x1152.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_800Wh-battery-297x223.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_800Wh-battery-120x90.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_800Wh-battery-768x576.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_800Wh-battery.webp 2000w\" /></a><figcaption>800Wh internal battery</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>New Bosch PowerTube options now also let you pick either 600Wh or 800Wh internal batteries – both smaller <em>and</em> larger range options than before. Plus, you can now add a 250Wh range extender external bottle battery to either setup to go even further.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_gen-5-Bosch-CX-motor.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_gen-5-Bosch-CX-motor.webp\" alt=\"2025 Focus Thron² versatile alloy all-rounder ebike all-mountain trail eMTB, Bosch Performance Line CX gen 5 motor\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_gen-5-Bosch-CX-motor.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_gen-5-Bosch-CX-motor-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_gen-5-Bosch-CX-motor-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_gen-5-Bosch-CX-motor-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_gen-5-Bosch-CX-motor-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_gen-5-Bosch-CX-motor-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_gen-5-Bosch-CX-motor-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>And wrap that all up with the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/boschs-new-performance-cx-ebike-motor-is-not-more-powerful-but-is-better-and-lighter/\" target=\"_blank\">newest gen 5 Bosch Performance CX motor</a> and you get an eMTB family with more useful and usable ebike power, easier hill starts, and much quieter operation.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_4-piston-Magura-ABS-anti-lock-brakes.webp\"><img width=\"1500\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_4-piston-Magura-ABS-anti-lock-brakes.webp\" alt=\"2025 Focus Thron² versatile alloy all-rounder ebike all-mountain trail eMTB, Magura ABS 4-piston brakes\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_4-piston-Magura-ABS-anti-lock-brakes.webp 1500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_4-piston-Magura-ABS-anti-lock-brakes-225x300.webp 225w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_4-piston-Magura-ABS-anti-lock-brakes-90x120.webp 90w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_4-piston-Magura-ABS-anti-lock-brakes-768x1024.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_4-piston-Magura-ABS-anti-lock-brakes-1152x1536.webp 1152w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_trail-capable-Bosch-ABS.webp\"><img width=\"1500\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_trail-capable-Bosch-ABS.webp\" alt=\"2025 Focus Thron² versatile alloy all-rounder ebike all-mountain trail eMTB, trail-ready ABS\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_trail-capable-Bosch-ABS.webp 1500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_trail-capable-Bosch-ABS-225x300.webp 225w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_trail-capable-Bosch-ABS-90x120.webp 90w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_trail-capable-Bosch-ABS-768x1024.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_trail-capable-Bosch-ABS-1152x1536.webp 1152w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The previous Thron² already had one EQP equipped model spec’d with anti-lock brakes. But now thanks to Bosch updating their ABS options for proper trail performance, most of the new Thron²s – both standard &amp; EQP models – come with more powerful brakes and ABS that you can adjust for your style of riding.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Tech details</h3>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_range-extender-battery.webp\"><img width=\"1500\" height=\"2000\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_range-extender-battery.webp\" alt=\"2025 Focus Thron² versatile alloy all-rounder ebike all-mountain trail eMTB, PowerMore range extender\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_range-extender-battery.webp 1500w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_range-extender-battery-225x300.webp 225w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_range-extender-battery-90x120.webp 90w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_range-extender-battery-768x1024.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_range-extender-battery-1152x1536.webp 1152w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://b