or.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-7-600Wh-768x461.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-7-600Wh.webp 2000w\" /></a><figcaption>2025 Focus Thron² 6.7 ABS with 600Wh battery</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-8-ABS-600Wh.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"922\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-8-ABS-600Wh-1536x922.webp\" alt=\"2025 Focus Thron2 versatile alloy all-rounder ebike all-mountain trail eMTB, 6.8 ABS\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-8-ABS-600Wh-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-8-ABS-600Wh-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-8-ABS-600Wh-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-8-ABS-600Wh-768x461.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-8-ABS-600Wh.webp 2000w\" /></a><figcaption>Thron² 6.8 ABS with 600Wh battery</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-9-ABS-800Wh.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"922\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-9-ABS-800Wh-1536x922.webp\" alt=\"2025 Focus Thron2 versatile alloy all-rounder ebike all-mountain trail eMTB, 6.9 ABS\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-9-ABS-800Wh-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-9-ABS-800Wh-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-9-ABS-800Wh-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-9-ABS-800Wh-768x461.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-9-ABS-800Wh.webp 2000w\" /></a><figcaption>Focus Thron² 6.9 ABS with 800Wh battery</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Thron² 6.7 starts at 4700€  with Shimano Cues 10-speed, SR Suntour suspension, and without ABS. The Thron² 6.8 ABS starts at 5300€ with Deore 12sp, RockShox Psylo Silver/Deluxe Select suspension, and anti-lock TRP Trail Evo brakes. Then, the 6700€ Thron² 6.9 ABS takes it one level higher with XT, Fox 36 AWL HD +Float Rhythm suspension, and Magura MT-C ABS brakes.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-7-EQP-600Wh.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"922\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-7-EQP-600Wh-1536x922.webp\" alt=\"2025 Focus Thron2 versatile alloy all-rounder ebike all-mountain trail eMTB, 6.7 EQP\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-7-EQP-600Wh-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-7-EQP-600Wh-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-7-EQP-600Wh-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-7-EQP-600Wh-768x461.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-7-EQP-600Wh.webp 2000w\" /></a><figcaption>2025 FocusThron² 6.7 EQP with 600Wh battery</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-8-EQP-ABS-800Wh.webp\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"922\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-8-EQP-ABS-800Wh-1536x922.webp\" alt=\"2025 Focus Thron2 versatile alloy all-rounder ebike all-mountain trail eMTB, 6.8 EQP ABS\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-8-EQP-ABS-800Wh-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-8-EQP-ABS-800Wh-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-8-EQP-ABS-800Wh-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-8-EQP-ABS-800Wh-768x461.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_thron2-6-8-EQP-ABS-800Wh.webp 2000w\" /></a><figcaption>Thron² 6.8 EQP ABS with 800Wh battery</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Thron² EQP comes in just 2 specs.  For 4900€, you get the Thron² 6.7 EQP with the pannier rear rack, headlight with high beam, kickstand &amp; full coverage metal fenders over 2.4″ Schwalbe Nobby Nic tires… all on top of the Cues 10sp drivetrain &amp; SR Suntour suspension. The 5500€ Thron² 6.8 EQP ABS does the fenders, rack, kickstand &amp; lights on top of a Deore 12sp build, SR Suntour suspension, and trail-ready Magura CT-ABS 4-piston anti-lock disc brakes.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_EQP-models-with-600-or-800Wh-batteries.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_EQP-models-with-600-or-800Wh-batteries.webp\" alt=\"2025 Focus Thron2 versatile alloy all-rounder ebike all-mountain trail eMTB, EQP riding\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_EQP-models-with-600-or-800Wh-batteries.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_EQP-models-with-600-or-800Wh-batteries-297x178.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_EQP-models-with-600-or-800Wh-batteries-1536x922.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_EQP-models-with-600-or-800Wh-batteries-120x72.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_EQP-models-with-600-or-800Wh-batteries-768x461.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>For any of the new 2025 Thron² models, upgrading from the 600Wh to 800Wh internal battery adds 300€ to the starting prices above. It just adds the slightly larger battery cover that you can see in the top-spec models above. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_rain-with-range-extender-battery.webp\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"1333\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_rain-with-range-extender-battery.webp\" alt=\"2025 Focus Thron2 versatile alloy all-rounder ebike all-mountain trail eMTB, with PowerMore external; battery\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_rain-with-range-extender-battery.webp 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_rain-with-range-extender-battery-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_rain-with-range-extender-battery-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_rain-with-range-extender-battery-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_rain-with-range-extender-battery-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_rain-with-range-extender-battery-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025-Focus-Thron2-versatile-alloy-all-rounder-ebike-all-mountain-trail-eMTB_rain-with-range-extender-battery-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The optional Bosch PowerMore 250Wh range extender will add around 460€.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.focus-bikes.com\" target=\"_blank\">Focus-bikes.com</a><br /><br /></p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2025-focus-thron%c2%b2-emtb-doubles-down-on-trail-riding-or-loaded-touring-commuting/\">2025 Focus Thron² eMTB Doubles Down on Trail Riding OR Loaded Touring &amp; Commuting</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Cory Benson","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"1f967dc1e1a8997d065b74e2c11c6f4985c41208a6c20c67ed766e5577b9f36b","category":"Cycling"}